  05 Jan 2015; Tupone Alfredo <tupone@gentoo.org> rockdodger-0.6.0a-r1.ebuild:
  EAPI 5

  15 May 2014; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> rockdodger-0.6.0a-r1.ebuild:
  Fix USE dependency on media-libs/libsdl, "audio" USE flag was renamed to
  "sound", bug 357661.

  20 Jun 2011; Tupone Alfredo <tupone@gentoo.org> rockdodger-0.6.0a-r1.ebuild,
  +files/rockdodger-0.6.0a-underlink.patch:
  Fix underlink. Bug #370129 by Diego Elio Pettenò

  09 Dec 2009; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org>
  rockdodger-0.6.0a-r1.ebuild:
  EAPI=2; add use-deps for sdl libs; honor CC and LDFLAGS

  29 Feb 2008; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org>
  rockdodger-0.6.0a-r1.ebuild:
  Remove icon extension from desktop entry to match Icon Theme Specification.

  24 Apr 2007; Timothy Redaelli <drizzt@gentoo.org>
  rockdodger-0.6.0a-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword.
  Thanks to Nathan Smith for reporting wrt bug #175779

  12 Mar 2007; Tristan Heaven <nyhm@gentoo.org> rockdodger-0.6.0a-r1.ebuild:
